'''''Star Wars Weekly'' 10''' is the tenth issue in the ''[[Star Wars Weekly]]'' series of comic reprints.

==Contents==
*[[Star Wars (1977) 5|''Star Wars'' (1977) 5]] {{C|Part 2}}
*"[[w:c:marvel:Marvel Preview Vol 1 1|Man-Gods from Beyond the Stars]]" {{C|Part 5}}
*"[[w:c:marvel:Marvel Preview Vol 1 7|The Sword in the Star! Stave 2: Witchworld!]]" {{C|Part 1}}

*"Cosmic Correspondence" {{C|letters column}}
*A contest to win a ''Star Wars'' watch. In order to enter, readers must match the pair of identical C-3PO's.

